ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectProvincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order No. 186, Manitoba
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 186 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the provision of financial assistance to the province of MANITOBA, with respect to the SEVERE FLOODING, that affected the province, from April 12, 2014 to July 11, 2014.
